      "message": "I tested this change manually on a local test site using [mailhog](https://github.com/mailhog/MailHog) and found the following issues\n- creating a new service user (without generating auth token or adding ssh key) doesn\u0027t send an email to the user who created it\n- creating an authentication token for a service user also sends an email to the service user, this shouldn\u0027t be done as service users will not read the email\n- adding an ssh key to a service user also sends an email to the service user, \n  this shouldn\u0027t be done as service users will not read the email\n- removing an ssh key from a service user doesn\u0027t send email",
